持曼聯的人，我真的會非常失望。因為我認為你可以在對手更有質量的時候輸波，但你不能因為對手態度比你好而輸波。所以，真的很失望<br />\n<br />\n爹哋覺得利記同曼聯質量一樣 <br />\n所以下定決心泊巴士求和<br />\n而觀眾又唔會失望<br />\n<br />\n曲線讚利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1082044a754f2e26fa3a538981061fab07ed70e0","tid":443770,"uid":9284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T02:43:40.000Z","msg":"屌晒上面笑曼既老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1474881ff06cd763c1206e1eac484989f869ee5","tid":443770,"uid":3194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T02:47:01.000Z","msg":"廢就廢啦垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ace5735c30df7664117482e45fbe97437e48f1c4","tid":443770,"uid":17116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T02:49:16.000Z","msg":"廢曼"},{"pid":"96df8027032737c64dd8cf07b7cd76af32ac8c9a","tid":443770,"uid":5163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T02:54:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ab8f10eecc844b9d19160f06d4821d15da4d17","tid":443770,"uid":90726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T03:04:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adb6611655be065023e7385ed94221b9b192d6d8","tid":443770,"uid":127466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-22T03:07:05.000Z","msg":"又 loopin